GUI :
    Main page : Buttons page of maulik
        Contacts Button : Opens second page showing all available contacts
        Add Button : Opens up a form page which takes all info
        Edit Button : It takes you to contacts screen and then you select one contact for edit.
            This will open up same form page with filled information.
        Groups button : Opens up a group page with only groups name, if clicked on any groups name
            then show the available contacts in that group.

